item.title: CVE-2021-34359|2024-09-17T01:12:01.133Z -- qnap%20systems%20inc. -- proxy%20server
item.description: A cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability has been reported to affect QNAP device running Proxy Server. If exploited, this vulnerability allows remote attackers to inject malicious code. We have already fixed this vulnerability in the following versions of Proxy Server: QTS 4.5.x: Proxy Server 1.4.2 ( 2021/12/30 ) and later
